publicwhip.spmotion: *S2M-3965 Scott Barrie: Dunfermline Crown Post Officeâ€”That the Parliament welcomes the news that the proposed franchise arrangement by the Post Office with CJ Lang & Son in Dunfermline has fallen through; believes that the proposal by the Post Office found no support from the people of Dunfermline, and congratulates the Communications Workers Union and others involved in the fight to save the Crown Post Office.
